title: No deadly terrorist attacks by people from countries covered by the restriction of entry abroad?
subtitle: It is alleged that a graph documenting that no foreign national from any of the seven countries listed in an executive order issued in January 2017 has killed any American citizen in the United States since 1975.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: There are graphic documents indicating that the nationals of the seven countries included in the restrictions on President Tramp ' s entry into the United States have not killed any American citizens since 1975.
